{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"final-quiz-8","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"期末冲刺","title":"期末冲刺练 第8题","difficulty":4,"tags":["有理数","倒数"],"content":"若 $a$ 与 $b$ 互为相反数，$c$ 与 $d$ 互为倒数，则 $2026a + 2025b + bcd = $______。","steps":[{"title":"解答","content":"$a + b = 0$，$cd = 1$\n$2026a + 2025b + bcd = 2026a + 2025b + b$\n$= 2026a + 2026b = 2026(a + b) = 0$","formula":"\\text{答案：}0"}]},"id":"final-quiz-8"},"__N_SSG":true}